我国已有8种新冠肺炎疫苗进行有效性评价，有望4月份完成临床前研究。
Eight new crown pneumonia vaccines have been evaluated for efficacy in China, and it is hoped that the preclinical study will be completed in April.
梁宙。
Liang Zhouzhou.
